Uses of Package
com.pandora.controllers.responsebodies.services

Packages that use com.pandora.controllers.responsebodies.services
Package
Description
com.pandora.controllers
Provides controllers for handling various HTTP endpoints related to biogeochemistry in freshwater environments within PANDORA.
com.pandora.controllers.responsebodies.services
The services subpackage under responsebodies contains service implementations related to processing and post-processing responses in the Pandora Freshwaters Biogeochemistry application controllers.
  • Classes in com.pandora.controllers.responsebodies.services used by com.pandora.controllers
    Class
    Description
    CellCalculationResponseService
    The CellCalculationResponseService interface defines the contract for services responsible for post-processing cell calculation responses and converting them into the appropriate format represented by CellCalculationResponse.
    SpeciesResponseService
    The SpeciesResponseService interface defines the contract for services responsible for post-processing species-related responses and converting them into the appropriate format represented by SpeciesResponse.
